author: Ben Kesslen
title: Newborn dies after mom with COVID-19 goes into preterm labor
description: "Had she not been COVID-19 positive... likely she would have not gone into preterm labor and there would have been a different outcome," the coroner said.
content:
A newborn baby in Louisiana died on Sunday after a mother with COVID-19 went into premature labor.
